{"tid":2244112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新研究曝：支那肺炎專殺A/AB血型易淪重症 O型血抵抗力最強","createTime":"2020-10-15T08:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T12:29:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c6809e94824163012c97c91b681d53a93d25e2b9","tid":2244112,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"丹麥與加拿大的研究團隊昨（14）日分別刊出最新報告，指出血型可能會影響患者感染新冠肺炎的機率與症狀，其中O型血感染新冠病毒的風險較低，病情也較不嚴重，A型與AB型血的人染疫風險較高，也有較高的重症比例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/Q3a90O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FQ3a90O&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzhTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=408842fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/Q3a90O</a>"},{"pid":"7af6290f5db832121b156e664726a6b80d31d5ee","tid":2244112,"uid":325023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:57:19.000Z","msg":"DNA取勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f5305149210211086a148f8157b83258fe22a1","tid":2244112,"uid":324629,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:02:25.000Z","msg":"終於俾O型血人士贏返一次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f2b6c9133e1b6f6c944194729aa7f14a685cef","tid":2244112,"uid":60057,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"O型血比例好似亞洲最高，歐美最低?<br />\n係唔係再一次證明隻毒係為殺歐美人而生"},{"pid":"9b40c2ed74be30ad184d96ba024a04f88738ab6a","tid":2244112,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01f2b6c9133e1b6f6c944194729aa7f14a685cef","tid":2244112,"uid":60057,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"O型血比例好似亞洲最高，歐美最低?<br />\n係唔係再一次證明隻毒係為殺歐美人而生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:19:59.000Z","msg":"Some blood types are more common in certain groups. Up to 53% of Latin Americans and 47% of African Americans have blood type O+. In comparison, only 39% of Asians, and 37% of Caucasians have this ty